een, Aayat 17]</h4>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\t\t</header><!-- .site-header -->\n\t\t<script language=\"javascript\" type=\"text/javascript\">\n\t\t\tvar cur_page_data = {pageid:\"8\", pagename:\"default-post\"};\n\t\t\tvar cur_themes_url = \"http://jamiat.joburg/site-data/themes\";\n\t\t</script>\n\t\t<div id=\"content\" class=\"site-content\">\n\n<div id=\"primary\" class=\"content-area\">\n\t<main id=\"main\" class=\"site-main\" role=\"main\">\n\t\t\n<article id=\"post-8\" class=\"post-8 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry\">\n\t<header class=\"entry-header\">\n\t\t<h1 class=\"entry-title\">Is your salaat up to standard</h1>\t</header><!-- .entry-header -->\n\n\t\n\t\n\t<div class=\"entry-content\">\n\t\t<div class=\"sm-row-fluid smue-row sme-dsbl-margin-left sme-dsbl-margin-right\">\n<div class=\"sm-span12 smue-clmn  sme-dsbl-margin-left sme-dsbl-margin-right\">\n<p><b>IS YOUR SALAAH UP TO STANDARD?</b></p>\n<p>Allah Ta`ala describes the Salaat of the Munaafiqeen as follows:</p>\n<p><b><i>When they stand up for salaah, they stand up lazily (reluctantly), (they perform salaah only) to show people and they remember Allaah only a little (they perform salaah very infrequently).</i></b></p>\n<p><b>CHECKLIST:</b></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Did you perform your wudhu meticulously?</li>\n<li>Are your clothing pure?</li>\n<li>Do you have the proper Headgear?</li>\n<li>Is your trousers above the ankles (men)?</li>\n<li>Are you concentrating in Salaah?</li>\n<li>Does your gaze wander about during Salaah?</li>\n<li>Are your postures correct?</li>\n<li>Are you reciting qiraat with proper Tajweed?</li>\n<li>Are your lips moving whilst reciting qiraat?</li>\n<li>Is your body properly covered?</li>\n<li>Are your earnings Halaal?</li>\n<li>Is your food Halaal?</li>\n<li>Are you dressed according to the Sunnat?</li>\n<li>Are you performing Salaat on its correct time?</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If any of your answers to the above are negative, then your Salaat is deficient. The more deficient your Salaat, the less reward you will earn. Let it not be that your Salaat is flung back at you for not being accepted. Take stock of your Salaat!</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sm-row-fluid smue-row sme-dsbl-margin-left sme-dsbl-margin-right\">\n<div class=\"sm-span12 smue-clmn  sme-dsbl-margin-left sme-dsbl-margin-right\">\n<div class=\"smue-text-obj\">\n<p>post 2</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\t</div><!-- .entry-content -->\n\n\t<footer class=\"entry-footer\">\n\t\t<span class=\"byline\"><span class=\"author vcard\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/2a292f79de62ec98417064d4a4611884?s=49&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g\" srcset=\"http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/2a292f79de62ec98417064d4a4611884?s=98&amp;d=mm&amp;r=g 2x\" class=\"avatar avatar-49 photo\" height=\"49\" width=\"49\"><span class=\"screen-reader-text\">Author </span> <span style=\"font-size: 15px; cursor:pointer\">ayugqoxu</span></span></span><span class=\"posted-on\"><i class=\"fa fa-calendar\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i><span class=\"screen-reader-text\">Posted on </span><a href=\"../blog/default-post.html\" rel=\"bookmark\"><time class=\"entry-date published\" datetime=\"2018-06-05T21:25:29+00:00\">June 5, 2018</time><time class=\"updated\" datetime=\"2018-06-06T22:43:44+00:00\">June 6, 2018</time></a></span>\t\t\t</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->\n</article><!-- #post-## -->\n\n\t<nav class=\"navigation post-navigation\" role=\"navigation\">\n\t\t<h2 class=\"screen-reader-text\">Post navigation</h2>\n\t\t<div class=\"nav-links\"><div class=\"nav-next\"><a href=\"../blog/no-title.html\" rel=\"next\"><span class=\"meta-nav\" aria-hidden=\"true\">Next</span> <span class=\"screen-reader-text\">Next post:</span> <span class=\"post-title\">Imaam Abu Hanifah</span></a></div></div>\n\t</nav>\n\t</main><!-- .site-main -->\n\n</div><!-- .content-area -->\n\n\n\t\t</div><!-- .site-content -->\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t<footer id=\"colophon\" class=\"site-footer\" role=\"contentinfo\">